md/raid5: Remove unnecessary bio_put() in raid5_read_one_chunk()

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.0.3 by commit 21a9c7354aa59e97e26ece5f0a609c8bfa43020d, it was introduced in version v5.14 by commit c82aa1b76787c34fd02374e519b6f52cdeb2f54b. For more details please see the references link.
